title: 8-MONTHS-PREGNANT MOM OF ONE shot execution style while cowering in bedroom closet. We want justice for Belinda Temple!
itunes:title: 8-MONTHS-PREGNANT MOM OF ONE shot execution style while cowering in bedroom closet. We want justice for Belinda Temple!
description:
For the second time, David Temple has been found guilty in the murder of his pregnant wife. Belinda Temple was just a month shy of delivery when she was shot in the back of the head. Joining Nancy Grace to look at the complexity of this case is Defense Attorney Jason Oshins , Forensic Expert Karen Smith, Psychologist Caryn Stark and Crime Online Reporter Dave Mack.
